  <h3>Authors</h3>

  <div class="well">
    <p>Create an author doc for each author. This lets us post social media links as part of each author's byline.</p>

    <p>Authors are matched to their content based on the full-name field.</p>
  </div>

  <form action="/author/edit" class="add_author" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded" method="get">
    <div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-xs">Add New</button>
    </div>
  </form>
  <ml:admin-author-list/>
</ml:page>
